<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Dance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天就是期待已久的萬聖節囉！<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />下工夫準備或許很辛苦，<delay20 />但今天就讓我們
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />連同努力的份，<delay20 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一起盡情享受這活動吧。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想你一定<delay8 />為今天的萬聖節
做好了萬全的準備<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />距離正式開始還有一段時間，<delay8 />
如果還有什麼事沒做完，<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就趁現在先辦好吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不知道今天的萬聖節
會是怎麼樣的活動？<delay8 />好期待喔～<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就算長大了，只要有活動<delay8 />就能跟你們一起嬉鬧，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我可以在這座島上生活，<delay20 />
真的很幸福喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你看，<delay20 />距離萬聖節開始<delay8 />
只剩一點時間了！<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />別忘了做好心理準備喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀，糟糕<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也差不多該去
做裝扮的準備了。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />還得補一下妝……<delay frames="30" /><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好忙啊～</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />萬聖節就快要拉開序幕了<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我們都要盡情享受，<delay8 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />留下美好的回憶喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="100" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">你知道這座島上
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有擺放<delay8 />使用了南瓜的裝飾嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那大概是為了萬聖節應景吧。
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然不知道是誰裝飾的，<delay20 />
我想那個人一定很重視
每個季節該有的感覺喔～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">我問你，<delay20 />你不覺得這座島的<delay8 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />南瓜裝飾越來越多了嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />大概是因為快到萬聖節了吧。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我自己也像個孩子一樣，<delay8 />
覺得興奮不已呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我問你，<delay20 />你有注意到嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />南瓜裝飾<delay8 />未免也太多了吧？<pageBreak /><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />南瓜裝飾的眼睛<delay8 />
彷彿看透了一切，<delay20 />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />讓人有點害怕呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />等等，這座島上的南瓜裝飾<delay8 />
未免也太多了吧？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看來有人非常期待萬聖節到來呢。
<anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過<delay8 />這心情我懂喔～
因為我也很期待<delay8 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />能從你那裡拿到糖果，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>